comments: The most helpful, easy professor I\'ve ever had so far. She makes the lab experiments and reports so easy and very clear. Although her class is an easy A, she makes the class fun and exciting while teaching at the same time. Very funny, easygoing. It\'s a shame I didn\'t try hard enough and ended up with a B in the class instead of an A . Recommended!

Shes awesome! Very helpful and wants you to pass. Gives extra credit and literally gives a step by step on how to get an A in the class and even holds your hand and walks you through it! You CANNOT fail with her!
Her lab is great!!! Take her she wants you to pass her class!! Shes cool too!!! Trust me you won\'t regret taking her class.
she is the best! take her, you will not be disappointed!
Really great teacher. Explains everything so you\'ll understand clearly and very helpful. You can\'t not a pass.
This professor is excellent. Extremely helpful and does not give answers, but gives handouts that help with the homework assignments. I would highly recommend this instructor. Makes learning fun.
Great professor, very understanding, makes class interesting. 2 field trips, 1 lab clean up, a little homework due each class, gives you the answers for work and homework.
Very cool, very chill. She made the class easy, and she\'s very approachable. She\'s also lenient with late work. I only took a 1 credit lab class with her, but overall it was a fun class.
